<header class="modal-header">
    <h1>即将删除该用户</h1>
</header>
<a class="close icon-x" href="" title="关闭" {{action "closeModal"}}><span class="hidden">关闭</span></a>

<div class="modal-body">
    {{#if user.count.posts}}
        <strong>警告:</strong> <span class="red">该用户是{{pluralize user.count.posts '篇文章'}}的作者，</span>您将要删除该用户的<strong>所有数据和文章</strong>。<br/>
    {{else}}
        <strong>警告:</strong>您将要删除该用户的<strong>所有数据</strong>。<br/>
    {{/if}}
    删除后无法恢复，是否确认？
</div>

<div class="modal-footer">
    <button {{action "closeModal"}} class="btn btn-default btn-minor">取消</button>
    {{#gh-spin-button action="confirm" class="btn btn-red" submitting=submitting}}确认{{/gh-spin-button}}
</div>
